<item>
            <title>[LU-18742] LustreError: statahead.c:2415:start_statahead_thread(): can&apos;t start ll_sa thread, rc: -4</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18742</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On a full 2.16.1 small production system (servers and clients), we keep seeing this occasional LustreError messages on clients:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Feb 21 08:48:09 elm-rcf-mr-h02s01 kernel: LustreError: 988403:0:(statahead.c:2415:start_statahead_thread()) can&apos;t start ll_sa thread, rc: -4&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I believe we have the default value for statahead_max (we&apos;ve seen crashes after increasing this value so we don&apos;t do that anymore, I should have reported those..):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
cat /sys/fs/lustre/llite/*/statahead_max
128&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>Rocky Linux 9.4</environment>
        <key id="87748">LU-18742</key>
            <summary>LustreError: statahead.c:2415:start_statahead_thread(): can&apos;t start ll_sa thread, rc: -4</summary>
