                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="445380" author="qian_wc" created="Sat, 22 Feb 2025 02:16:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The error message with rc=-4(EINTR) during statahead thread launch means that it failed to start a stat-ahead thread.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I do not think this is a Lustre stat-ahead bug.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Maybe it is related to the kernel that does not have enough resource to launch a kernel thread?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="445373" author="pjones" created="Sat, 22 Feb 2025 00:09:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yingjin&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you please advise?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
